      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean and presents well, showing only minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical for a car of its age. Inside, the cabin is comfortable and well-kept, with some light wear on the driver's seat bolster but no tears or unpleasant odors. It runs smoothly and all major features are fully functional, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver. Potential buyers can expect a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for properly over the years.",
