    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and running perfectly. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s ready for a new home. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
