    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 high-revving inline-six, boasting meticulous valve clearances and a fully serviced VANOS system for precise variable valve timing. The chassis has received proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity against torsional stress. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the communicative steering and neutral handling balance this platform is renowned for. This is a mechanically flawless, turn-key example for the purist who demands surgical precision and an uncompromised service history.",
      "price": 46500.0,
