    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show absolutely no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory floor mats are pristine. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, with the infotainment screen still retaining its crystal-clear clarity. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. This is a collector-grade piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. No accidents, no modifications, and no stories\u2014just a flawless driving experience.",
